text:
09 U.S. Navy to China: We’ll sail our ships near your man-made islands whenever we want 
The Washington Post: U.S. officials could soon send a Navy ship steaming by a chain of man-made islands that China has built in the South China Sea, Pentagon officials said, potentially exacerbating tensions in an area in which Beijing is expanding its presence.
